<main>
    <section class="ig-hero"><div class="ig-wrap"><div class="ig-copy"><div class="ig-kicker"><span class="platform-icon" data-platform-icon="instagram"></span>Instagram for business</div><h1>Turn Instagram attention into qualified leads.</h1><p>Answer enquiries quickly, capture what each customer needs, and move serious buyers closer to a sale.</p><div class="ig-actions"><a class="ig-btn ig-btn-primary" href="{{ auth()->check() ? route('dashboard') : route('register') }}">Turn conversations into leads →</a><a class="ig-btn ig-btn-light" href="#how">See how it works</a></div></div></div><div class="ig-statbar"><div class="ig-wrap ig-stats"><div><strong>Every lead</strong>kept in one inbox</div><div><strong>Always on</strong>for first enquiries</div><div><strong>Your team</strong>closes the sale</div></div></div></section>
    <section class="ig-section" id="how"><div class="ig-wrap"><div class="ig-intro"><h2>Every comment can start a customer relationship.</h2><p>MYinboxLAB gives your team the context and speed to turn public interest into a helpful private conversation.</p></div><div class="ig-grid"><article class="ig-card"><div class="num">01</div><h3>Reply where attention happens.</h3><p>Catch questions in comments and move the right people into DMs without losing the thread.</p></article><article class="ig-card"><div class="num">02</div><h3>Welcome the next follower.</h3><p>Give new followers a warm, useful first response instead of another silent notification.</p></article><article class="ig-card"><div class="num">03</div><h3>Keep the human touch.</h3><p>Let the assistant handle routine conversations while your team steps in when intent gets serious.</p></article></div></div></section>
    <section class="ig-section ig-faq" id="faq"><div class="ig-wrap"><h2>Instagram questions, answered.</h2><div class="ig-faq-list"><details class="ig-faq-item"><summary>Can it reply to Instagram comments?</summary><p>Yes. The Instagram workflow is designed to help your team handle public comment intent and continue the conversation privately where appropriate.</p></details><details class="ig-faq-item"><summary>Can I control what the assistant says?</summary><p>Yes. Add your services, pricing, availability, policies, tone, and escalation guidance in the workspace knowledge and AI settings.</p></details><details class="ig-faq-item"><summary>Will I still see the full customer history?</summary><p>Yes. The conversation stays in the shared inbox so your team can see the message context and take over whenever judgment is needed.</p></details><details class="ig-faq-item"><summary>Do I need a separate Instagram app?</summary><p>No. Connect your Instagram professional account through the MYinboxLAB workspace, subject to Meta account permissions and review requirements.</p></details></div></div></section>
</main>
